Class-Variable
==============

Perl implementation of class variables with access restrictions.

    Documentation on CPAN:
        http://search.cpan.org/~hurricup/Class-Variable/lib/Class/Variable.pm
        
    Documentation on MetaCPAN
        https://metacpan.org/pod/Class::Variable

    Testing results
        http://www.cpantesters.org/distro/C/Class-Variable.html
        
    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Class-Variable

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Class-Variable

INSTALLATION
============

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

